		SIF GROUPMATCH(FLAG:역극, [[첸]], [[란]], [[유카리]])
			RETURNF PLACE_ID
		SIF CFLAG:[[유카리]]:동실 && (TALENT:[[유카리]]:연모 || TALENT:[[유카리]]:사모)
			RETURNF PLACE_ID
	;仙人の屋敷・書斎
	CASE 724
		SIF PERMISSION
