		;역극/住んでる/사모以上동실で許可
		SIF FLAG:역극 == [[카센]]
			RETURNF PLACE_ID
		SIF INRANGE(CFLAG:MASTER:초기위치, 720, 730)
			RETURNF PLACE_ID
		SIF CFLAG:[[카센]]:동실 && (TALENT:[[카센]]:연모 || TALENT:[[카센]]:사모)
			RETURNF PLACE_ID
