		SIF PERMISSION
			RETURNF PLACE_ID
		;역극/住んでる/동실で許可
		SIF GROUPMATCH(FLAG:역극, [[텐시]], [[이쿠]])
			RETURNF PLACE_ID
		SIF INRANGE(CFLAG:MASTER:초기위치, 834, 842)
			RETURNF PLACE_ID
		SIF CFLAG:[[텐시]]:동실 || CFLAG:[[이쿠]]:동실
